WEBVTT

00:11.943 --> 00:13.924
I am crippled because of
my loyalty to you.

00:13.960 --> 00:15.844
You are crippled
because it's God's will.

00:15.880 --> 00:18.198
I'm offering you
a second chance, Gawain.

00:18.234 --> 00:20.954
[BOTH GRUNTING]

00:21.047 --> 00:23.155
King Philip demands you vacate
the Holy See.

00:23.241 --> 00:26.330
But the means of your removal...
Well, he left that up to me. [BONES CRACK]

00:26.366 --> 00:27.766
LEADER:
<i>Solvet Saeclum in favilla.</i>

00:27.829 --> 00:30.314
[ALL GRUNTING]

00:30.377 --> 00:31.602
DRAPER: Quentin's dead.

00:31.675 --> 00:34.110
I have an even more vital task
for you.

00:34.671 --> 00:35.714
[GROANS]

00:37.116 --> 00:39.462
FATHER VALENTIN: The Baptismal
Rolls, Your Grace? [BABY CRYING]

00:39.525 --> 00:40.973
[SWORD UNSHEATHES]

00:41.839 --> 00:42.659
[SIZZLING]
Aah!

00:42.730 --> 00:44.966
- Who did this to you?
- I did it to myself.

00:45.002 --> 00:46.172
Don't lie to me,
brother.

00:46.226 --> 00:47.346
There is no place
in the Temple

00:47.401 --> 00:49.307
for a man who will betray
his brothers.

00:50.979 --> 00:53.363
[WIND HOWLING]

00:53.399 --> 01:00.830
♪♪

01:00.866 --> 01:08.338
♪♪

01:08.738 --> 01:10.632
[BREATHING HEAVILY]

01:10.668 --> 01:11.655
♪♪

