TANCREDE:
Open the gates!

01:47.602 --> 01:48.776
Open the gates!

01:48.812 --> 01:51.315
[INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS]

01:54.844 --> 01:56.888
Open the gates!

01:59.000 --> 02:01.210
[GROANING]

02:03.505 --> 02:05.410
TANCREDE:
Open the gates!

02:05.476 --> 02:07.312
[CHICKEN CLUCKING]

02:10.184 --> 02:11.735
Quickly, open it up.

02:13.339 --> 02:15.758
[GATE CREAKS]

