39:10.848 --> 39:12.480
Aah!

39:12.516 --> 39:14.399
[HORSE NEIGHS]

39:14.435 --> 39:16.027
[BODY THUDS]

39:16.063 --> 39:18.321
[GROANING]

39:18.357 --> 39:20.364
[HORSE NEIGHS]

39:20.400 --> 39:24.847
♪♪

39:34.013 --> 39:35.473
[GROANING]

39:40.228 --> 39:41.485
[BODY THUDS]

39:41.521 --> 39:43.617
- [GROANS]
- I didn't give you permission

39:43.681 --> 39:47.233
to leave the Temple grounds,
Initiate.

39:47.559 --> 39:49.936
I didn't plan
on coming back.

39:51.811 --> 39:53.444
I wanted to die here.

39:53.480 --> 39:56.615
I didn't give you permission
to do that, either.

39:56.651 --> 39:58.116
[BREATHING HEAVILY]

39:58.152 --> 40:00.827
Well, isn't this
[GROANS]

40:00.863 --> 40:03.456
what you would call
a noble death?

40:03.492 --> 40:06.626
Death is never
your choice to make.

40:06.662 --> 40:09.754
Only God decides
whether we live or die.

40:09.790 --> 40:12.132
God has abandoned me.

40:12.168 --> 40:15.218
God doesn't care if I live
or die, so why should I?

40:15.254 --> 40:16.345
[GROANS]

40:16.381 --> 40:20.511
God has not
abandoned you.

40:23.112 --> 40:25.663
He's given you instruction

40:25.714 --> 40:29.307
on how to mend
your troubled soul.

40:29.437 --> 40:32.316
He has guided you here
to this place

40:32.383 --> 40:36.684
to protect your young
Initiate Brothers.

40:36.862 --> 40:41.307
God's light shines in you,
and even your sins,

40:41.362 --> 40:46.666
no matter how great,
could ever extinguish that.

40:46.832 --> 40:48.130
[CHUCKLES]

40:48.166 --> 40:51.510
♪♪

40:51.546 --> 40:54.930
After the fall of Acre,

40:54.966 --> 40:57.516
I was taken prisoner

40:57.552 --> 41:01.312
for nearly 10 years.

41:01.348 --> 41:04.399
They took everything
from me,

41:04.435 --> 41:09.571
and when I had nothing left
to live for,

41:09.607 --> 41:11.824
I prayed for death.

41:11.860 --> 41:15.870
I begged God
to relieve my suffering,

41:15.906 --> 41:20.542
to take me home
to my fallen brothers.

41:20.578 --> 41:23.254
But He didn't.

41:23.290 --> 41:26.132
And to this day,

41:26.168 --> 41:29.970
I believe there is a reason
He spared my life.

41:30.006 --> 41:34.850
♪♪

41:34.886 --> 41:37.722
When there's nothing
to hold on to...

41:40.301 --> 41:42.392
...hold on to your faith.

41:42.561 --> 41:49.074
♪♪

